fields.description: Vision about the gods of Babylon
fields.body:
In the dream, the veil of reality seemed to thin, and before me was a sprawling sea, its turquoise waters shimmering under the radiant sun. The vast expanse stretched as far as the eye could see, meeting the sky at the horizon and creating an endless panorama of serene blue. Waves crashed against the shores rhythmically, as if each one was the heartbeat of the earth itself.

Suddenly, the surface of the water quivered and, one by one, the Babylonian deities began to emerge. Their ethereal forms were resplendent and their presence, even in the dreamscape, was awe-inspiring. They were as imposing as they were ancient, their very existence transcending the boundaries of time.

First was Marduk, the supreme deity, his resplendence illuminating the surroundings. In his hands, he held the tablets of destiny, the sea seemingly bowing to his will. Ishtar, the goddess of love and war, followed him. Her fierce beauty was accentuated by the fiery aura around her and the sea around her surged with her powerful energies.

Enki, the god of water and wisdom, came next. The sea calmed as he surfaced, recognizing one of its own. His eyes held an ancient wisdom, the kind you can only acquire by witnessing the changing tides of time. Tiamat, the goddess of the sea, emerged beside him, her form an amalgamation of the sea and the cosmos, chaotic yet mesmerizing.

As the procession continued, more deities appeared - Ea, the clever god of magic and wisdom, Nanshe, the goddess of social justice and prophecy, and Sin, the god of the moon, their forms as resplendent as they were diverse. The sea, the sky, the sun, the moon, everything seemed to acknowledge their presence, their power. They stared into the sea, their eyes reflecting the ancient wisdom and secrets hidden in its depths.

In this dream, the gods were not detached and distant, they were tangible, connected to the world, part of its rhythm, part of its cycle. They were custodians of knowledge, a testament to the universe's past, present, and future. The dream was not just a window to the divine but a mirror to the cosmic cycle of creation and destruction, a celebration of the eternal dance of the cosmos.

In the dream, I stood at the edge of an expansive city, teeming with lights and vibrant life. The golden hues of the setting sun played across the sky, casting long shadows over the labyrinth of steel and glass. From the distance, the city was a marvel of human achievement, a testament to our resilience and innovation.

Suddenly, the air shifted, the temperature dropping so quickly that it sent a chill down my spine. Above, the sky darkened, a thunderous rumble reverberating through the firmament as storm clouds gathered with unnatural speed. The city's bright lights flickered and then dimmed, replaced by an uneasy twilight.

A fear, both raw and primal, stirred within me. An insidious feeling that something was wrong, something was coming. The earth under my feet began to tremble, and from the depths of the city, I heard the sound of alarms, a cacophonous symphony that echoed my own rising panic.

And then, they appeared. Figures materialized from the city's skyline, enormous and imposing. They were not of this world, their forms inhuman and terrifyingly alien. Their mere presence felt like a violation, a grotesque interruption of the world as we knew it. They moved with horrifying grace, each step they took towards the city making the earth quake.

The city's inhabitants ran in fear, their panicked screams swallowed by the monstrous figures’ deafening roars. They moved through the city, their grotesque forms silhouetted against the burning skyline. Their intent was clear: destruction. They were the embodiment of danger, a cataclysmic force threatening to annihilate humanity.

But even amidst the chaos, there was a flicker of hope. I looked towards the city again, and among the fleeing crowd, I saw figures rising, their faces set with grim determination. They were ordinary people, but in this moment of crisis, they were becoming something more. They were preparing to fight, to protect their city, their home.

As I woke up, the images of the dream lingering, I realized its message. The danger was imminent, yes, but so was the opportunity for heroism and resilience. It was a call to action, a warning of a trial by fire, but also a testament to our capacity to face adversity. The dream was a reminder that danger and calamity often bring out the best in us, forcing us to unite, to fight, and ultimately to prevail.

fields.title: MORNING DEVOTION
fields.speaker: SPO
fields.message: 📌 WATCH OUT FOR ATTACKS As I began praying this morning, I saw evil spirits like time wraiths in the The Flash movie come out from a pit in the ground, and I heard "darkness, darkness is coming". I saw these spirits transform into humans and enter places of fame, recognition and power. I normally say a little prayer before reading my Bible, but today I was led to pray concerning blindness, deafness, ignorance and selfishness. As I prayed concerning blindness and deafness, I got the impression of a spirit of slumber that has been released, and will slowly cause blindness. I got that how he will do this will be by causing us to sleep during devotions and church meetings, and then we will be ignorant of what was taught and not see what we were meant to see. I also got laziness, and an ability to overlook things. I saw a family gathering, and discussions were going on. I also saw a spirit who took note of what it saw and heard, hide behind their bookshelf. This evil spirit was to report back on that family, and it seemed it had been assigned to that family. While I prayed concerning ignorance, I got the impression of not being aware of situations and matters on ground, and behaving as though all is well. It also seemed to be linked to the spirit of slumber that had been sent out. While I prayed concerning selfishness, I got "thoughts about self alone increases pride, and decreases access to God." Then I heard: "My people are not ready for what's coming on them. I've shown you, can you please tell them? It's bad, it's so bad. I'm raising up the dead, let the living be more active”. [I got the impression that this 'dead' refers to buried giftings, authority and mantles]. "Let them put their gifting to more work, there's much land to be conquered. If you don't do it fast, the Canaanites will remain there permanently and oppress the people I have there. Gentiles everywhere, pleading for help The heathens are clamouring for salvation But how can they be saved if nobody has been sent there? So I'm sending you, go and bring them to Me Go God's Lighthouse, and bring them to me."

fields.title: Dream
fields.speaker: E.N
fields.message: We were in a building that had a Catholic church setting (the main meeting hall and the vestry) and we were all waiting for the Lord. We had gotten instructions that JESUS was coming and we all gathered in the meeting hall, waiting. It was for the purpose of an exam, a sifting exam and the only way of this sifting process was seeing the Lord. This exam was to be done in batches. So while we were waiting, 2 sisters started having prophetic experiences, the other just kept crying, while the other was shocked and she kept saying ' The Lord is Here, JESUS HAS COME, JESUS IS HERE. This was a confirmation that it was time for us to be examined. So the invigilator took the first batch into the vestry (room of focus and no distraction). We were to pray to see the Lord and meet HIM in that room, when you see him, you leave the room and like Moses's face, the evidence of meeting the Lord was there. After praying for awhile, i remember a sister leaving the room glowing saying - I have seen Him. After a while, others came out saying the same thing after seeing the Lord, including a sister that just came to join us, in a sense she was new. After the time had elapsed, the invigilator who was dressed in a priestly garment came to take those remaining who had not seen the Lord out of the vestry. The determinants for not seeing the Lord were: 1. How we despised personal Bible study and deprived ourselves of seeing the Lord personally. So he urged us to go back and do better. 2. Service: Those that are working, and how dilligent one has been in their work and lastly those having the ability to work more but refusing to do so. 3. Seeing the Lord was not a function of how long you've been in here. Those that have seen the Lord were upgraded to the Holy Place, that was the reason of the sifting.

fields.title: Glossallia Prayer Point -MORNING DEVOTION
fields.speaker: HN
fields.message: An impression... While we prayed for Pastor Ita and his family, I saw him in a conference room. He was sitting on a chair and before him(on a table) was a piece of paper. Then I saw that around his ear region(besides both ears) were illustrations depicting radio signals. When those signals would show up, Pastor would pause, listen and then ponder on whatever information was gotten before putting it into writing. I had the impression he was transmitting and receiving vital information through these waves and needed total concentration. At some point, a lot of babies/toddlers were allowed into the conference room. I had the impression that these little children were God's Lighthouse members and their need for unnecessary attention. They came around the space where he was sitting and they were all over him(playing with him and the book that was on the table). Pastor's heart couldn't resist them(send them away) so he tried to make sure they could stay around him(by keeping them calm and steady) while receiving the signal from his own end. At some point, everything seemed to be going on well until there was a break in transmission- at first, the radio waves became shaky but with time, the signals eventually disappeared. I had the impression that he lost focus because the children couldn't stay still after all he had done to ensure they did...

fields.title: Apostolic Education Day 5 Prophetic Word by Favour O
fields.speaker: FO
fields.message: 24th December 2023 Saturday Tarry Meeting FO While Pastor prayed for me, I saw an angel slowly approaching me. He was big, probably the biggest personal angel I've ever seen. He held an eyeball in each but they were more like large shining crystals, all I saw were orbs of light but I knew they were eyeballs. I stretched out my hands to receive them but he just stopped a few feet away and stared at me with vacant white shining eyes. He seemed to analysing me but he didn't speak. Later I saw that we were in an underground area made entirely of stones. It looked like the dungeons in ancient stone castles but I was later told this was the 'Archive area.' I walked with the angel by my side and our movements were a bit glitchy, like appearing some steps ahead without actually moving your feet. It took me a while to realise we weren't walking at all, just gliding on air and translocating in short steps. I saw myself pushing a hidden stone door he instructed me to go through, but it was too heavy for me and barely moved. I called out to the angel to help me and he moved the door by simply leaning his hand on it. We walked into a wider area also enclosed by stone walls but there was a pool of water in the room. All this while I was asking the angel to give me the eyes but he never answered me a word. Instead he circled to the other side of the pool and indicated (without words) that I should walk across the water and meet him there. I gradually and deliberately made myself land on the ground and took a step on the water. It was cold and sent shivers through my soul. As I put one foot in front of the other, I saw crowds of people screaming through the water, crying for help and stretching upwards. What came to mind was how bodies of water represent the nations/people. As I walked on the water, I gradually began to sink with each step. From the feet to the ankles, then up to the knees and so on. By the time the water reached my chest, I was crying as though my chest was being crushed and it felt like that. Finally I sunk completely under the water I was at the other side of the pool and the angel silently reached in and pulled me out of the water. He put the crystal eyeballs into my hands, they sunk into the palms and moved up to the wrists. He took my hand and led me somewhere else, I realised that as soon as he gave me the new eyes, I went blind so I needed to be led. Finally the angel began to speak to me. He asked if I wanted to see the dead and indicated a stone door nearby. I looked inside and saw a group of people standing around and some were playing cards. There was an inner door but I wasn't sure so I humbly declined the invitation to enter. We went to another area where there were shelves full of ancient looking scrolls, some on the table and ecen on the ground. Some were half opened, half read but most were still closed and sealed. I went to the table where a scroll was half opened and pushed it all the way open. It was a map of the world but in live 3D, the diagrams were moving. I saw three massive ships sail across the Atlantic ocean, heading towards Europe. They looked like aircraft carriers but much bigger and they didn't stop at the coast. These ships crashed into the European nations and levelled them to the ground as they passed through. I was told that these three ships were three nations, and they would try to conquer the world. I thought of France being one of them but they were also affected by the devastation of the ships. I saw a head of state making a speech, he looked like Vladimir Putin, president of Russia, but older. At the same time, he looked like Joe Biden, president of the United States of America. Though I couldn't hear the speech, I knew it was an official declaration of war. I saw fighter jets taking off and other advanced armaments moving into position. I heard, "where are your own weapons?" The voice sounded deeply offended and a bit sad. He spoke of how he had released 50 jets 50 years ago to the fathers, but they had dismantled them and sold the parts for money. I saw the jets in question, they were big planes actually, like Boeing 747s but fully armed and fast like bomber jets. I saw them parked and dismantled from the wings, wheels, cockpit and engine parts, carted off to be sold. The voice spoke about 36 nations rising to crush the world, having forged their weapons with blood in their secret places. But the side of God were lacking weapons because the fathers sold them off. I saw a city surrounded by a very high and wide wall but the Watchmen were all missing. The Watchmen were also 36 in number and He said that in five years, all 36 Watchmen would die off. "Watch and observe, 36 Watchmen are about to die."
